          "title": "A BETTER UNDERSTANDING OF 3D SCENES OVER TIME",
          "summary": "ResFields is a new kind of neural network that's really good at understanding complex 3D scenes as they change over time. By adding something called 'temporal residual layers,' it can deal with a lot more information and still stay accurate.",
